Builder Design Pattern

IS used for constructing a complex object from simple objects using step by step approach. It is
mostly used when creating a complex item can't easily be done in one step.

Advantages
1)  It provides clear seperation between the construction and representation of an object.
2)  It provides better control over construction process.
3)  It supports to change the internal representation of an object

Steps
1)  create a Packing interface.
2)  create 2 abstract classes CD and Company
3)  create 2 implementation classes of Company: Sony and Samsung
4)  create the CDType class
5)  create the CDBuilder class
6)  create the BuilderDemo class